* TABLE :: Personal pronouns
  - stand-alone forms and suffixed forms
 
  |--------+--------+-----------+-------------+----------|
  | Person | Number | Gender    | Stand-alone | Suffixed |
  |--------+--------+-----------+-------------+----------|
  | 1st    | sing.  | --        | men         | -en      |
  | 2nd    | sing.  | --        | teps        | -eps     |
  | 3rd    | sing.  | Sapient   | teth        | -eth     |
  | 3rd    | sing.  | Insapient | sos         | -os      |
  | 1st    | plur.  | --        | menen       | -enen    |
  | 2nd    | plur.  | --        | tepsen      | -epsen   |
  | 3rd    | plur.  | Sapient   | tethen      | -ethen   |
  | 3rd    | plur.  | Insapient | sosen       | -osen    |
  |--------+--------+-----------+-------------+----------|

  - RULE :: to form the suffixed form, drop the initial consonant

