 | dafodîleneps      | your daffodils          | Nominative plural | 2sing possessor |
 | dafodîlenepsen    | your all's daffodils    | Nominative plural | 2plur possessor |
 | dafodîlôdheps     | to your daffodil        | Dative singular   | 2sing possessor |
 | dafodîlôdheneps   | to your daffodils       | Dative plural     | 2sing possessor |
